[normal] for 
[normal]penalizing
[normal] 
[normal]those
[normal] 
[normal]who
[normal] 
[normal]evade
[normal] VAT. A national 
[normal]legal
[normal] system 
[normal]may
[normal] 
[normal]choose
[normal] to 
[normal]fulfil
[normal] 
