[normal] State 
[normal]against
[normal] 
[normal]which
[normal] the 
[normal]applicant
[normal] 
[normal]seeks
[normal] to 
[normal]apply
[normal] 
[normal]it
[normal]. Article 2 
[normal]safeguards
[normal] 
[normal]against
[normal] 
[normal]this
[normal] 
[normal]reading
[normal], by 
[normal]making
[normal] 
[normal]it
[normal] 
[normal]clear
[normal] 
[normal]that
[normal] the right or 
[normal]principle
[normal] must 
[normal]be
[normal] 
[normal]recognized
[normal] in the 
[normal]law
[normal] of the UK. 
[normal]Whether
[normal] 
[normal]that
[normal] 
[normal]is
[normal] 
